    "body": "There are 3 differents cases here:\r\n- connecting to mailserver (up to 100 attemps), means it might work in a moment\r\n- mailserver disconnected, I am not sure what this one will mean because we only request messages after login so if mailserver disconnects after sending us the messages we missed it doesn't really matter.\r\n- no peers connected, you won't even be able to send messages so quite similar to No network\r\n\r\nI find `Messages connection problem` very vague, at this point maybe we should just say `Error: Can't (send and) receive messages, please restart the app` ?",
